《'''梅迪亞萬聖節'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Boo! A Madea Halloween'''''}}）是一部於2016年上映的[[美國|美國]][[喜劇片|喜劇]][[驚悚片|驚悚片]]，由[[泰勒·派瑞|泰勒·派瑞]]執導、編劇、主演，並與Ozzie Areu、Will Areu共同擔任監製。電影的概念取自虛構角色{{le|梅迪亞|Madea}}與[[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]的2014年電影《[[喜劇人生|喜劇人生]]》<ref>{{cite web |last=Hipes |first=Patrick |url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/boo-a-madea-halloween-from-top-five-idea-to-2016-release-1201686117/ |title=Lionsgate Slates ‘Boo! A Madea Halloween’ Based On ‘Top Five’ Idea |publisher=Deadline |date= |accessdate=2016-01-21 |archive-date=2016-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121060011/http://deadline.com/2016/01/boo-a-madea-halloween-from-top-five-idea-to-2016-release-1201686117/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本片為「黑瘋婆系列電影」的第八部作品，同時也是該系列第二部非[[舞台劇|舞台劇]]改編的電影（第一部為2012年的《{{le|黑瘋婆的證人保護計劃|Madea's Witness Protection}}》）。該片定於2016年10月21日在北美上映。

== 劇情 ==
故事敘述梅迪亞大媽在萬聖節大開殺戒，殺的是在萬聖節出沒的鬼魂與喪屍軍團<ref>{{@movies|id=fben65325452|title=梅迪亞萬聖節 Boo! A Madea Halloween}}<!-- 2016-11-04 accessdate --></ref>。

== 反響 ==
=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於32篇評論，持有的新鮮度僅22%，平均得分3.7／10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/boo_a_madea_halloween |title=Boo! A Madea Halloween (2016) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-10-29 |archive-date=2016-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028211752/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/boo_a_madea_halloween |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]基於14篇評論，獲得30分，負評居多<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/boo!-a-madea-halloween |title=Boo! A Madea Halloween |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2016-10-27 |archive-date=2016-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107221712/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/boo!-a-madea-halloween |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間約落在「A」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |accessdate=2020-09-11 |archive-date=2002-09-14 |archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20020914132118/https://www.cinemascore.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，觀眾的反應比影評人好上許多。

=== 票房 ===
該片在美國於2016年10月21日上映，預計首週末能從兩千兩百六十間中獲得1500萬至1700萬美元的票房<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/10/the-accountant-ben-affleck-kevin-hart-fall-box-office-ticket-sales-1201835284/ |title=Can Ben Affleck’s ‘The Accountant’ Be An Asset For Weak Fall Box Office? – Preview |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2016-11-04 |archive-date=2016-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017193510/http://deadline.com/2016/10/the-accountant-ben-affleck-kevin-hart-fall-box-office-ticket-sales-1201835284/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=budget>{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-movie-projector-20161018-snap-story,amp.html |title='Jack Reacher: Never Go Back' to battle 'Ouija' sequel and 'Boo! A Madea Halloween' at box office |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |accessdate=2016-11-04 |archive-date=2016-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019081223/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-movie-projector-20161018-snap-story,amp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影在首映當天獲得940萬美元的票房，首映週末總計2760萬美元，位居當週票房冠軍，表現超乎預期，這成為[[泰勒·派瑞|泰勒·派瑞]]第四高的首映票房<ref name="nty34">{{cite web | url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-box-office-report-boo-madea-20161022-snap-story.html | title='Boo: A Madea Halloween' scares up a win at the box office while 'Jack Reacher' nabs a close second | publisher=''Los Angleles Times'' | date=2016-10-22 | accessdate=2016-10-23 | archive-date=2016-10-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161023140704/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-box-office-report-boo-madea-20161022-snap-story.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Prev">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/10/weekend-box-office-jack-reacher-tom-cruise-keeping-up-with-the-joneses-ouija-madea-tyler-perry-1201840348/|title=‘Madea’ To Push Well Past $27M As ‘Jack Reacher’ Takes $22M to $23M; ‘Joneses’ Can’t Keep Up – Sun. AM Update|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=2016-10-23|accessdate=2016-10-23|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610015323/https://deadline.com/2016/10/weekend-box-office-jack-reacher-tom-cruise-keeping-up-with-the-joneses-ouija-madea-tyler-perry-1201840348/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第二週獲得1720萬美元（僅39.6％的跌幅）的票房，且儘管面臨新片《[[地獄_(2016年電影)|地獄]]》（1490萬美元），《梅迪亞萬聖節》仍持續保持其冠軍寶座<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4235&p=.htm |title='Inferno' Takes on the World Series as 'Doctor Strange' Debuts Overseas |work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |accessdate=2016-11-04 |archive-date=2016-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102212708/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4235&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

